<eesti>Ravikulude katmine </eesti>
<inglise>Covering of Costs of Medical Treatment </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Terviseuuringute ja ravi eest tasumine </eesti>
<inglise>Payment for medical examination and treatment </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kindlustatu terviseuuringute, tervise s&auml;ilitamise ja ravi kulud, v&auml;lja arvatud visiiditasu, tasub haigekassa temaga lepingu s&otilde;lminud ravi- v&otilde;i hooldusasutusele v&otilde;i erapraksisega tegelevale arstile, olenevalt osutatud teenuste hulgast ja hinnast. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The costs of medical examinations, medical treatment and the preservation of the health of an insured person, except visit fees, shall be paid by the health insurance fund to the relevant medical or care institution or private physician, if the institution or physician has entered into a contract with the health insurance fund, proceeding from the volume of services provided and their cost. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud teenuste hinnad ja teenuste eest tasumise korra kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus sotsiaalministri ettepanekul koosk&otilde;las Eesti Haigekassa seaduse &sect; 12 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti 2 s&auml;tetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The prices for the services specified in subsection (1) of this section and the procedure for payment for the services shall be established by the Government of the Republic on the proposal of the Minister of Social Affairs in accordance with the provisions of clause 12 (1) 2) of the Estonian Health Insurance Fund Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(14.06.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2001 - RT I 2000, 57, 374) </eesti>
<inglise>(14.06.2000 entered into force 01.01.2001 - RT I 2000, 57, 374) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Arsti vastuv&otilde;tule soovija maksab raviasutusele v&otilde;i erapraksisega tegelevale arstile visiiditasu, mille suuruse ning maksmise ja isikutele kompenseerimise korra, samuti sellest laekunud summade kasutamise korra kehtestab Sotsiaalministeerium. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The size and the procedure for compensation of the visit fee to be paid to the medical institution or private physician by a person wishing to consult a doctor, and the procedure for using the money received thereby, shall be established by the Minister of Social Affairs. </inglise>
<eesti>(22.03.94 j&otilde;ust.01.04.94 - RT I 1994, 23, 387) </eesti>
<inglise>(22.03.94 entered into force 01.04.94 - RT I 1994, 23, 387) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Haigekassa h&uuml;vitab apteekidele soodustingimustel v&auml;ljastatavate ravimite soodustuse m&auml;&auml;ra sotsiaalministri poolt kehtestatud ulatuses ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The health insurance fund shall compensate pharmacies for the rate of discount on medicinal products distributed at a discount, to the extent and pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Social Affairs. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.12.98 j&otilde;ust.01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.12.98 entered into force 01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kindlustatutele apteekidest soodustingimustel v&auml;ljastatavate ravimite loetelu, selle koostamise ja korrigeerimise korra kehtestab sotsiaalminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The list of medicinal products distributed to insured persons at a discount at pharmacies and the procedure for the preparation and amendment thereof shall be established by the Minister of Social Affairs. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.12.98 j&otilde;ust.01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.12.98 entered into force 01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Ravimi kandmisel kindlustatutele apteekidest soodustingimustel v&auml;ljastatavate ravimite loetellu l&auml;htutakse ravimi t&otilde;estatud meditsiinilisest efektiivsusest ja ravimi kasutamise majanduslikust p&otilde;hjendatusest. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The inclusion of a medicinal product in the list of medicinal products distributed to insured persons at a discount at pharmacies shall be based on the proven efficacy of the medicinal product and on the economic justification for using the medicinal product. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.12.98 j&otilde;ust.01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.12.98 entered into force 01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Ravimi kandmise aluseks kindlustatutele apteekidest soodustingimustel v&auml;ljastatavate ravimite loetellu on ravimitootja taotlus koos t&auml;iendava dokumentatsiooniga, mille esitamise korra kehtestab sotsiaalminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The basis for the inclusion of a medicinal product in the list of medicinal products distributed to insured persons at a discount at pharmacies is an application from the manufacturer of the medicinal product together with supporting documentation, the procedure for the submission of which shall be established by the Minister of Social Affairs. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.12.98 j&otilde;ust.01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.12.98 entered into force 01.01.99 - RT I 1998, 111, 1829) </inglise>
