<eesti>(2) Kindlustatu soovil j&auml;tab raviarst t&ouml;&ouml;andjale esitatavale t&ouml;&ouml;v&otilde;imetuslehele diagnoosi m&auml;rkimata. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) At the request of the insured person, the attending physician shall not indicate the diagnosis on the certificate of incapacity for work to be presented to the employer. </inglise>
