<eesti>Ravikindlustusega seotud vaidlused </eesti>
<inglise>Disputes concerning health insurance </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse kohaldamisel tekkinud vaidluste lahendamiseks v&otilde;ivad pooled p&ouml;&ouml;rduda kohtusse kolme aasta jooksul, arvates p&auml;evast, mis j&auml;rgnes p&auml;evale, mil nad said teada v&otilde;i oleksid pidanud saama teada oma &otilde;iguste rikkumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order to resolve disputes which arise in the application of this Act, the parties may have recourse to a court within three years after the date following the date on which they became aware or should have become aware of a violation of their rights. </inglise>
